  </section>

  <section id="access" data-reveal>
    <h2>4. Access and Availability</h2>
    <p>We aim to keep the Site available and accurate, but we do not guarantee uninterrupted, error-free, or secure access. We may suspend, withdraw, or restrict all or any part of the Site for maintenance, security, or operational reasons without notice.</p>
  </section>

